@NODE NEWS "SCENE NEWS !!!"

 @{fg highlight}@{b}[-------------------------( Scene-News )---------------------------]@{ub}@{fg text}
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 The Last Swede joined iFFTic. His independent days are gone!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Slash/Citron. became a good friend to iFFTic after leaving us.
 Maybe we both did ourselves a favour by splitting up?
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 The Vote-Door went out to 6 boards again, without takin a break
 for a month, like we use to do. New boards were Total Eclipse and
 Trancentral. City of JoY and Crime Zone were the ones to stand back!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Total Disaster had a UL-compo with 60 mb to the winner!
 Juan&harpoon fought hard, but Yogi/iTc was impossible to match!
 J&H finish second and got 30 mb for that, and noone came in third!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Sandman of Epsilon Design released his fourth ascii-collection,
 it was called "the fourth dimension of ascii" and included clip-art!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 A stupid Nazi-propaganda Amiga-guide called Gryning were spread by
 guys with more attitude than brains! Most boards nuked it hard!,
 but Rebel of Trancentral felt that the freedom of speech included
 this one and allowed it to live on.
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Dagcentral 90210 opened up again and announced it with big adds,
 promising 3 nodes. It stayed up a day or 2 and it had only 1 node!
 After a week it was up again, but right now it's down again!
 I wonder if it's the same Node that goes down and up? :-()
 The guys behind it are Zwinx and Rage, so the rumours that it should
 be Biotech/iTc who would open it up again, proved themselves wrong!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Cabbe & Master joined accounts and are now Cabbe ^ Master.
 They are franchising for Livets Ord & and are after your soul!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Total Eclipse now runs on an a1200 and a new HD, a Western Digital.
 -A big step for humanity :) going from tiny 86 mb to now 420 Mb!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Total Eclipse now also have the essential Blizzard 1220 Memory-card.
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 City of Joy became the first board in town to run on a 28.8 DS modem
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 West became the second board in town to get a 28.8 DS modem
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Unicorn got a bigger HD of 540 mb, all together now 780 mb to fill!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Unicorn also got a new faster modem, it's a USR terbo 21.6! (upgradeable)
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Crime Zone got a new Hd with 540 Mb and some more ram-memory as well.
 Still just 1 node. Someone just hate these adds with 46-31-SooN/eLiTE!!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Ul-Compo at Trancentral, 50-30-10 Mb to the winners, heavy competition
 at first between Sandman and Zcandaler with Magma securing the third place.
 But then something fucked up, Weektops with wrong bytes made S & M upset
 and Zcandaler who were lucky, sailed away on a solo-ride and won the Compo.
 Lots of confusion and mishaps in this compo, so no accusations to anyone,
 except maybe the Sysop, who didn't break in and clearified the situation!
 There is still no presentation of the results, so only the ones who won
 some of the bytes are able to really know. ( I can tell you from my own
 experience that I got 10 Mb and that Sandman told me he got his Mb's! :)
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Yeah! Dexter made it! Total Disaster now runs on a GVP G-FORCE 030!
 May the speed be with You, young man! (more Ram memory is on the way too!)
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 The Baron of DefJam agreed to join iFFTic at the last minute of finishing
 up this chart! DefJam will be kept somehow for sentimental reasons,
 but iFFTic will be the main flag for him and his board now! Wow another
 iFFTic board too? Yes! it's true! West BBS is now the iFFTic Drive-In.
 And when we say Drive-In, it's not just for a cool name!, cause West Now
 has the Serialport locked at 115600. & accepts v.Fast, v.Terbo, v.34, etc.
 So there's no need to park your modem outside - bring it in!  C U there!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 Dagcentral 90210 has been up for some days now... Latest News Rulez!
 @{FG FILL}@{B}·@{FG TEXT}@{UB}
 @{fg highlight}@{b}[-------------------------( Scene-News )---------------------------]@{ub}@{fg text}

@ENDNODE

@NODE FUTURE "THE FUTURE OF THE SCENE !!!"

 A look on what's happening Now! & A guess for the Future!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}
 Pd-stuff is flooding the Elite-boards. One Sysop already counts it
 as around 60% of all warez traded on his board. If we would class all
 freely spread stuff like Ascii-collys, Text-files, Demos, intros,
 Music-Disks, Modules, and so on as in the Public Domains too,
 even 60% might be an understatement
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 And it was only like less than 6 months ago, that you easily could
 call a good PD-board and get some fresh PD, that you could upload on
 an Elite-board. But nowadays all PD hits the Elite-boards about a week
 before it arrives through the different Nets to your local PD-board!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 And the trend is lesser and lesser Cracks, so don't expect this
 to change back all by itself...
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 The CC's is harder and harder to get, and if you get them they won't
 last like they used to. Virgin my ass is a common expression lately!
 It's now impossible to call out of Sweden with any Mci-cards too.
 They shut that opportunity down for some unknown reason. And I bet
 that all the writings in NewsPapers and the discussions on NewsShows
 in TV about kids cheating with telephone-cards won't make it better!
 So expect AT&T to get smarter and the free calling to get harder!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 This all means that the rule of 0-2 days warez might be history soon!
 Cause how can we expect guys to deliver the goods as fast and as vivid
 if they have to pay the overseas call all by themselves? The warez will
 come, Yes, but not like it used to! So be prepared both Sysops & users!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 The reason for lesser Cracks and maybe also lesser demo-coding might be
 the lazyness of humanity. I mean when the elite of these 2 knowledges
 started out, they had the "boring" C-64 and similar machines that didn't
 offer much software or ready-made fun! So they had the natural inspiration
 to make it happen by themselves! But nowadays when you buy your first
 computer, you will get lots of interactive entertainment as a bundle.
 And I believe that cramps the lust of making your own stuff, cause you
 will be busy playing great games or using software "for dummies"!
 I hope I'm wrong on this, but the trend says the opposite!
 And the scene is full of all those Gamers now!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 There will still be group-releases of commercial games, Yes!
 And the software Industry might still skip the copy-protections,
 cause they have learned it to be useless anyhow, when there were great
 crackers out there. So don't inform them if this changes to the bad!
 A guess is that many of the future releases will be bought Games without
 copy-protection! And that the new way of joining a group won't depend on
 your skills, but more if you can afford to go and buy a new Game that
 your group can release under their name!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 So if all this happens, there's only trading skills that can keep us elite!
 Anyone calling PD-boards knows how sad it feels to see the way they trade;
 old and new files mixed, strange descriptions in mixed swedish and english
 and often missing vital information - just check pictures, and then there
 is no support to depend on for the latest versions of important software,
 cause everything drops in if the users feel for it, I mean PD-boards are
 the dream for Leechers! And that's why it's no fun to engage oneself in
 those boards! I like a vibrant scene where the callers can feel that some-
 thing happens... Not a PD-board where you only can see who leeched last!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 I want Latest Versions Only! Correct descriptions, and your upload-bytes
 faked/taken if you manage to screw up on any of these two conditions!
 Then there is the Request Area for the rest and one Message-base only,
 not 50 different, so you can't change the subject in a conversation!
 That's the only way I like to trade! Otherwise I can't be bothered!
 Please! Add your own opinion to this, cause the future is closing in!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}׳@{ub}@{fg text}
 MgM/iTc 02-Okt-94  20:48:24.

@ENDNODE

@NODE WARNING "WARNING, WARNING !!!"
 
 @{B}@{FG FILL}WARNING TO BOARDS:@{UB}@{FG TEXT}

 @{fg highlight}iFFTic is doing this Chart as a Service to our own Scene,@{fg text}
 but it often feels like noone thanks us, and that a lot demands
 this and that from us... @{fg highlight}So we just want to make a statement:@{fg text}

 @{b}Boards that are badly managed doesn't deserve to be in the Chart@{ub},
 and that's what will happen in the future!

 @{B}@{FG FILL}BAD MANAGEMENT LIKE:@{UB}@{FG TEXT}
 Sysops that are Eremites, and never call out themselves,
 Sysop that don't support their own board, not even in a crisis,
 CoSysops that are even more passive than the Sysop,
 CoSysops that's just a name and don't even call the board,
 HQ's that are just a Name and nothing more...
 No or very slow replys on letters from Sysops,
 No check on files, not even on suspicious ones,
 Acceptance of lousy file-descriptions,
 Bulletins that don't exist or never gets updated,
 Commands that are "unknown commands" for ages,
 Harddrives that gets full too often,
 Rules on the board that are not practiced in reality,
 Nuked bytes that are not returned to the downloaders,
 Sysops who doesn't protect the user's PW from friendly eyes,
 Sysops revealing private infos from the quest to other users,
 Sysops allowing harassment of their own users...

 Boards that allows nazi-propaganda or childporno to be spread will also
 (Yes, I know that no normal board on earth has or even wants childporno,
 I just mention it, to fulfill the massmedial myth, @{FG FILL}-hi aftonbladet!@{FG TEXT} :)
 get removed, cause who wants to cut off the branch we all are sitting on?
 Stupid Newspapers and so on should not be able to fabricate any more
 false articles from any board that's in the iFFTic Chart! We allow people
 to be Nazis in their Private, cause that's a democratic right and should
 always be so, but it's a another thing to have it out in the open with
 users having nazi-propaganda in their Locations or in their Sent-Lines,
 or to write public messages that supports nazi-views or similar.

 @{B}@{FG FILL}BOARDS THAT COULD SHAPE UP:@{UB}@{FG TEXT}

 A-BASE - BAD OR NO MANAGEMENT!
 CRIME ZONE - PASSIVE MANAGEMENT!
 TOTAL DISASTER - NAZI-VIBRATIONS! (Yes! only vibbs, sofar!)

 MgM/iTc 02-Okt-94  22:53:03.

@ENDNODE

