 IT HAS COMPLETE FACTS LIKE EVERYTHING THERE'S TO KNOW ABOUT A FILM - BUT
  NOT ON ALL 18.000 TITLES, IT'S FAST ENOUGH  - IT TAKES 5MB OF YOUR HD
   IT'S REALLY FRESH SO EVEN 1994-FILMS THAT ARE STILL PLAYING ARE IN!
      IT HAS A LEXICON-PART, INDEPTH INFOS AND SOME PICTURES AS WELL
        AND IT WILL GET UPDATED ALL THE TIME. IT'S DANISH FREEWARE!
         (vty_mg31.dms, vty_mg32.dms, vty_mg33.dms, vty_mg34.dms)

                       @{b}MGM@{ub} (NO, NOT GOLDWYN!) @{b}941005@{ub}

  @{fg highlight}@{B}׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳@{fg text}@{UB}
